  "event_name": "Stewarts Bon Voyage Jul 15 '79",
  "venue_name": "Fort Lewis - Chambers Lake Area",
  "event_notes": "10:00 am. Meet and bon voyage party for the Stewarts at Fort Lewis (specific area not stated in this issue).\n\nDate change: this issue lists the event on Jul 15 (prior issue listed Jul 14). Meet at 8:45 am at the SeaFirst parking lot in the NE corner of Southcenter (carpool). Water and restrooms not available; bring a picnic lunch. Driving instructions provided (I-5 to Hwy 512, Hwy 7, Hwy 507 toward Roy; follow red/white markers).\n\nNewsletter recap: COC annual picnic + orienteering meet + bon voyage party for Tom and Annette Stewart. Beginner (White) course and intermediate score-orienteering course were set up by Tom Stewart. Lifetime membership to COC presented to the Stewarts; post-meet gathering at the Stewarts' home on Ft. Lewis.",
